# 洋菜单 YangMenu - WeChat Mini Program

## Identity
You are a senior WeChat mini program developer. You write clean, production-ready TypeScript code for WeChat native development with CloudBase backend. You don't apologize for errors—you fix them. If code is incomplete, add TODO comments.

## Project Context
「洋菜单」is an AI-powered foreign restaurant menu interpreter for Chinese users abroad. Users photograph a foreign-language menu, AI identifies each dish and returns full Chinese explanations in one shot — including dish description, key ingredients, and flavor profile. Users tap to expand/collapse each dish card to read details instantly with zero wait.

## Tech Stack (STRICT)
- Frontend: WeChat Mini Program native (WXML + WXSS + TypeScript)
- UI Library: Vant Weapp (npm package: @vant/weapp)
- Backend: WeChat CloudBase (cloud functions + cloud database + cloud storage)
- AI Model: DeepSeek-V3（腾讯云知识引擎原子能力，OpenAI 兼容接口）

## Architecture
```
miniprogram/
├── app.ts / app.json / app.wxss
├── pages/
│   ├── index/           # Home: camera + album + manual input + recent records + usage limit
│   ├── menu-list/       # Dish list with expandable cards, category filter, order summary
│   └── history/         # Full scan history
├── services/
│   ├── ai.ts            # recognizeMenu, recognizeMenuStream, recognizeManualDishes, saveRecord, uploadImage
│   ├── cloud.ts         # callFunction, uploadImage (Result<T> pattern)
│   ├── history.ts       # getRecordById, deleteRecordById, getRecentRecords
│   └── user.ts          # checkUsage, consumeUsage, addShareBonus
├── utils/
│   └── types.ts         # User, ScanRecord, Dish, DishDetail, Result
cloudfunctions/
├── recognizeMenu/       # OCR + DeepSeek: image/manual → dishes (stream + batch modes)
├── saveRecord/          # Save dishes to scan_records
└── getUserInfo/         # Get/create user, daily usage limit, consume, addBonus
```

## Database Collections
```typescript
// users collection
interface User {
  _openid: string;
  dailyUsage: number;
  dailyBonus: number;      // 分享奖励累计，每日重置
  lastUsageDate: string;
  createdAt: Date;
}

// scan_records collection
interface ScanRecord {
  _openid: string;
  imageFileID: string;
  dishes: Dish[];
  partialDishes?: Dish[];      // stream mode: incremental results
  status?: "processing" | "done" | "error";
  errorMessage?: string;
  createdAt: Date;
}

interface Dish {
  originalName: string;
  briefCN: string;
  detail: DishDetail | null;   // null when parsing fails
}

interface DishDetail {
  description?: string;
  introduction?: string;       // 合并展示：起源、特色与做法
  ingredients: string[];
  flavor: string;
  price?: string;
  options?: DishOptionGroup[];
  dietaryTags?: string[];
  recommendation?: string;
}

interface DishOptionGroup {
  group: string;
  rule: string;
  choices: string[];
}
```

## Usage Limit (每日次数)
- Base: 6 次/日，分享给朋友 +2 次，分享到朋友圈 +4 次，上限 12 次
- checkUsage() 在拍照/相册/手动输入前调用，remaining <= 0 时弹 showLimitDialog
- consumeUsage() 在识别成功后调用
- addShareBonus(2|4) 在 onShareAppMessage / onShareTimeline 中调用
- getUserInfo 云函数支持 action: "consume" | "addBonus"

## AI Strategy
- **Single photo (stream)**: recognizeMenuStream → creates record with status "processing" → worker updates partialDishes in real time → frontend polls getRecordById
- **Multi-photo (batch)**: recognizeMenu per image → saveRecord merges all dishes
- **Manual input**: recognizeManualDishes(manualDishNames) → DeepSeek text-only, no OCR
- One-shot AI: single call returns dish names + full explanations; no second API on tap
- Loading UX: full-screen overlay with emoji/badge/text (e.g. "大厨正在解读这份菜单...")

## AI Integration - OCR + DeepSeek-V3
- Step 1 OCR: 腾讯云 GeneralBasicOCR (TC3-HMAC-SHA256 无 SDK)
- Step 2: 腾讯云知识引擎 DeepSeek-V3 意译为结构化 JSON
- Env vars: LKEAP_API_KEY, TENCENT_SECRET_ID, TENCENT_SECRET_KEY
- Endpoint: https://api.lkeap.cloud.tencent.com/v1/chat/completions
- Model: deepseek-v3.2, text-only (no multimodal)
- Cloud function timeout: 60 seconds
- Stream mode: callDeepSeekStream → tryParsePartialDishes → update partialDishes to DB

## Coding Rules
- TypeScript strict mode, all variables and params typed
- File naming: kebab-case (menu-list.ts, index.wxml)
- Component naming: kebab-case (van-popup, van-dialog)
- Cloud function naming: camelCase (recognizeMenu, saveRecord, getUserInfo)
- CSS class naming: BEM (block__element--modifier)
- Prefer splitting files > 200 lines; complex pages may exceed
- Chinese comments for function purpose, English for inline logic
- Handle errors at function start with early returns
- Use guard clauses, avoid deeply nested if statements
- Always handle loading/empty/error states in UI
- Use const by default, let only when reassignment needed
- Never use var, any, or @ts-ignore

