## Key Business Logic
- Usage limit: 6 base + share bonus (max 12), enforced via getUserInfo
- Auth: wx.login + getUserInfo cloud function → openid
- Multi-page menu: up to 6 photos per session
- Image validation: size <= 4MB, format jpg/jpeg/png
- Image compression: wx.compressImage (quality 50, compressedWidth 960) before upload
- Manual input: parseManualNames supports 逗号/分号/顿号/换行分隔，最多 40 道菜
- Expand/collapse: tap dish card to toggle detail, _expandedKeys Set for state
- Category filter: inferDishCategory (沙拉/汤品/意面/烩饭/炖菜/烤物/牛排/披萨/汉堡/三明治/炸物/寿司/煎饼/面包/冷盘/派/海鲜/饮品/鸡肉/猪肉/羊肉/咖喱/塔可卷饼/小食/甜点/其他)
- Order summary: _orderMap, add/decrease per dish, order bar, order detail panel with scroll-to-dish
- pendingRecord: app.globalData 缓存 record，供 menu-list 直接使用，避免二次请求

## Vant Components Used
van-button, van-cell, van-cell-group, van-icon, van-image, van-loading, van-toast, van-empty, van-tag, van-action-sheet, van-overlay, van-popup, van-dialog

## App Config (app.json)
- lazyCodeLoading: "requiredComponents"
- enableShareAppMessage, enableShareTimeline: true
- permission.scope.userLocation: 用于识别城市，提供更精准菜品文化背景

## Don'ts
- No cross-platform frameworks (Taro, uni-app)
- No unnecessary npm packages
- No direct AI API calls from frontend (must go through cloud functions)
- No mock data or placeholder content — connect to real APIs
- No review/rating/social features (not in MVP)
- No image generation features (not in MVP)
- No localStorage for important data (use cloud database)
